# /var/lib/krb5kdc/kadm5.acl — kadmind ACL.
#
# Grants the bootstrap admin principal full rights over all principals.
# nova-api uses kadmin.local (not kadmin), so ACLs do NOT gate the API
# server's principal CRUD; they only matter for remote kadmin clients.
#
# Replace NOVANAS.LOCAL at deploy time if a non-default realm is in use.

nova-kdc-admin/admin@NOVANAS.LOCAL  *
